{"tid":1718697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行人路路面不平？係唔係路政署失職？要call 1823投訴了！","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T15:35:46.000Z","uid":41423,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ea8c5433e2466cf63bb3d60efddca33b316241","tid":1718697,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:05:51.000Z","msg":"大家呢幾個月行行人路，會唔會覺得凹凸不平，行得唔舒服？<br />\n就算條路鋪晒板，硬係好耐都唔鋪磚/石屎做番平路？<br />\n有無試過無左路面標誌，搞到自己失盪失路？<br />\n同埋行人路竟然無左圍欄同埋欄杆？等間唔小心失足跌左落馬路咁點算？<br />\n<br />\n一條完整既行人路，同交通標誌對所有行人同道路使用者都係甚至社會運作都十分重要！！<br />\n  <br />\n其實咁樣即係有政府部門失職？相關政府部門當然要負責啦。<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以去路政署個網頁投訴同report既：<br />\n道路損毀或欠妥報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/enquiries_and_complaints/report.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fenquiries_and_complaints%2Freport.php&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=e3f85814\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/enquiries_and_complaints/report.php</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然用電腦網上report比較user friendly, 但原來路政署係1823其中一個參與部門！！<br />\n即係可以用1823 app, 去到邊，見到有以上情況，影低相/片就可以投訴路政署冇做好本份/監督contracter維修道路！路政署做得慢，要比個deadline 佢，搵埋申訴專員公署投訴路政署失職！<br />\n希望大家都盡市民責任！令行人路/道路修復工程加快完成！"},{"pid":"60584a4d865ddb2272eaaedf8937b30c615eedf0","tid":1718697,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"唔想行路突然仆街就要report!"},{"pid":"3c7a231b2d744740f145073116ec7b566c1de51a","tid":1718697,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e0f1250fb3d1905ea9f9c51b3cba0c742393ca3f","tid":1718697,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"da3c750517d2d4428e3d0d3706384eb872d2bc9f","tid":1718697,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"25d596da83ebf1f0a7b6e2548bb8fd6a06843055","tid":1718697,"uid